                            <div class="text">
                                <p><b>Balaji</b> is the founder of <b>Rudram Sanatanam</b> Foundation. With a deep interest in spirituality and inner well-being, he established the foundation to share the benefits of yoga, meditation, and Sanatan Dharma teachings with society. </p>
                                <p>The vision of the founder is to contribute towards building a healthier, peaceful, and spiritually awakened society by reconnecting individuals with the timeless wisdom of Sanatan Dharma, inspired by the principle <i><b>"Sarve Jana Sukhino Bhavantu"</b></i> (May all beings be happy).</p>
                                <p>The foundation was established with the intention of creating a space where individuals can rediscover inner harmony through the practices of yoga, meditation, shiva consciousness and spiritual learning.</p>
                                <p>By sharing ancient knowledge in a simple and practical way, the foundation aims to help individuals lead balanced and meaningful lives.</p>
